    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. While the engine does turn over, it runs roughly and has several fluid leaks that need immediate repair. The body shows heavy wear including noticeable rust on the rocker panels and various dents, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a source for parts, as it is not currently in roadworthy condition.",
